full_title: BIRDS OF A FEATHER by Billie Eilish
title: BIRDS OF A FEATHER

description.plain:
In “BIRDS OF A FEATHER,” Billie expresses a belief in enduring love that persists until the end of life. She describes it as a powerful connection that remains resilient through challenges and emphasizes her desire for her partner to be by her side for eternity.

Billie and her brother FINNEAS, who collaborated on the song, described the song as a deep exploration of the overwhelming emotions tied to attachment and commitment. They revealed that during the song’s creation process, they initially overcomplicated the song’s message but ultimately streamlined it. Billie emphasized that the meaning behind the track is intentionally left open, inviting listeners to find their own interpretations to the song.

The song was officially teased by Netflix as an exclusive snippet in the trailer for Season 3 of the popular Netflix series Heartstopper.
